{"tid":245823,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"做廚真係狗也不屌?","createTime":"2017-05-16T14:08:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-17T22:10:54.000Z","uid":475,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a6e40e49d91b10c2298e946e9afaab36ec947073","tid":245823,"uid":475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T14:08:18.000Z","msg":"最近裸辭左份19會計 想轉行<br />\n上網同朋友都聽到做飲食真係好惡做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁其實實質即係邊part惡頂?<br />\n講惡頂係咪多數都係讀唔成書逼住做 根本就冇咩興趣係到呻吟定咩?<br />\n<br />\n前景又點呢?如果淨係講走fine dinning or 酒店西餐<br />\n<br />\n如果零飲食經驗 點入行同新仔應該大約咩價位?<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打可以分享下?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:u grad 冇屋企經濟負擔 2~3年日日煮幾人飯既經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  對廚有興趣"},{"pid":"2f4bfcef9c590041c779cc96924bc9fc1d1558a1","tid":245823,"uid":98060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T14:11:32.000Z","msg":"你預入行萬二到萬四，呢行成日有人走，如果叻既好快升到職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：抄散一名"},{"pid":"72d28a913864dc02811fc13e462282bd0dd3bbcb","tid":245823,"uid":475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T14:15:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你預入行萬二到萬四，呢行成日有人走，如果叻既好快升到職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：抄散一名</blockquote><br />\n如果白紙入去 叫萬3 大唔大機會請?定係識人先呢個價?"},{"pid":"11830a2c41e3595423e3bb095601aeea9d545fd1","tid":245823,"uid":98060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T14:33:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你預入行萬二到萬四，呢行成日有人走，如果叻既好快升到職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：抄散一名</blockquote><br />\n如果白紙入去 叫萬3 大唔大機會請?定係識人先呢個價?</blockquote><br />\n絕對有可能到萬三位 不過我會建議你唔好去大公司做 人事好麻煩更多假少人工少"},{"pid":"17b1e0a7bc343233719463a83396bf7cfdc19242","tid":245823,"uid":117292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T14:33:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"